__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Claude Code / agent session state and worktrees (local only, not for sharing)
.claude/

# macOS
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

# Editor / misc
*.swp
*~
.idea/
.vscode/

# Firmware images are NOT tracked: the stock image is Line 6's copyrighted
# property and the patched image is a derivative work. They live here locally
# and are reproducible with build/build_firmware.py from your own stock copy.
# Ignore EVERYTHING under firmware/ (any name/extension) except the README, so a
# stray or mis-extensioned image can never slip in.
# To track an image anyway (e.g. a private repo): git add -f firmware/<name>
firmware/*
!firmware/README.md
